kala-timeserver (0.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Automatic serial console disabling for GPS use
  * Uses raspi-config for proper serial port configuration
  * Notifies user when reboot is required
  * Improved GPS hardware setup automation

 -- Seth <seth@raspberrypi>  Thu, 05 Sep 2025 14:15:00 +0000

kala-timeserver (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added GPS/PPS support for Raspberry Pi Ultimate GPS HAT
  * Added gpsd, gpsd-clients, pps-tools, python3-gps dependencies
  * Auto-detects GPS hardware and configures appropriately
  * Includes both standard and GPS-enhanced chrony configurations
  * Automatic UART configuration for GPS communication

 -- Seth <seth@raspberrypi>  Thu, 05 Sep 2025 14:00:00 +0000

